        <name>Open RPM</name>
        <summary>Raven's Progressive Matrices IQ Test</summary>

        <description>
                <p>Open RPM is a modern implementation of Raven's Progressive Matrices (RPM) - a standardized non-verbal intelligence test. This application provides a complete 60-question test with age-adjusted IQ calculation and detailed results analysis.</p>
                <p>Features:</p>
                <ul>
                        <li>60 progressive matrix questions across 5 series (A-E)</li>
                        <li>20-minute timed test with progress tracking</li>
                        <li>Age-adjusted IQ calculation using spline interpolation</li>
                        <li>Detailed diagnosis and recommendations</li>
                        <li>Series-by-series analysis with deviation tracking</li>
                        <li>Multi-language support (English, Russian, Indonesian)</li>
                        <li>Modern GNOME interface with GTK4 and Libadwaita</li>
                </ul>
        </description>

